{{Quote|Your Masters may have told you lies about me, or they may have told you nothing. It does not matter. I have nothing to tell to them.|[[Daenerys Targaryen]] to the slaves of Meereen|Breaker of Chains}}

The '''Great Masters''' are the ruling elite of the city of [[Meereen]], one of the three cities of eastern shores of [[Slaver's Bay]], composed of [[Slavery|slave-traders]].
